prompts.frontCover: A whimsical, dreamy fantasy anime-style birthday card front, flat 2D artwork. A slightly grumpy but endearing cartoon gnome, wearing a pointy red hat and a blue tunic, is struggling to carry an absurdly large, glowing, magical birthday cake that is tilting precariously. The cake is decorated with sparkling pastel frosting, edible stardust, and tiny, mischievous forest sprites who are gleefully nibbling on the icing. The scene is set in an enchanted forest clearing at twilight, with oversized, softly glowing mushrooms, detailed flowering vines, and fireflies dancing in the air, creating a magical atmosphere. In the center, written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Johnny". The overall color palette is soft pastels, evoking a charming, lighthearted, and enchanting fairy-tale quality.
